Comment: Hi everybody, just to continue my theme of making blunders under pressure this time it is my buddy dmaestro who is on the receiving end.  A lot of the time dmaestro has caused me many problems and I have suffered from serious passivitis against him so I am glad to give something back here!  I kick off with c4 which is the English Opening.
